section.para:
Clicking an ID with the left mouse button will insert it into the buffer;
clicking with the right mouse button will move the caret to the element
that declares it.

listitem.para:
        Added caching of schemas and completion info in memory.
        It can't be turned off.
        It retains cached objects until :


all requiring buffers are closed;

the file is opened in jEdit;

the file is closed in jEdit;

the file is modified in jEdit.
